com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models

Class PeekMessagesOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.QueueServiceOptions
      • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.PeekMessagesOptions

  • public class PeekMessagesOptions
extends QueueServiceOptions
    Represents the options that may be set on a peekMessages request. These options include a server response timeout for the request and the number of messages to peek from the queue.
